[
  {
    "startTime": 12.559,
    "endTime": 13.44,
    "text": "so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.44,
    "endTime": 15.839,
    "text": "sometimes i get angry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.839,
    "endTime": 17.52,
    "text": "and it took me many years to be able to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.52,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "say just those words"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 21.6,
    "text": "in my work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.6,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "sometimes my body thrums i'm so enraged"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 28.88,
    "text": "but no matter how justified my anger has"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.88,
    "endTime": 31.76,
    "text": "been throughout my life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.76,
    "endTime": 34.079,
    "text": "i've always been led to understand that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.079,
    "endTime": 36.88,
    "text": "my anger is an exaggeration a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.88,
    "endTime": 38.559,
    "text": "misrepresentation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.559,
    "endTime": 42.399,
    "text": "that it will make me rude and unlikable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.399,
    "endTime": 45.92,
    "text": "mainly as a girl i learned as a girl"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.92,
    "endTime": 48.8,
    "text": "that anger is an emotion better left"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.8,
    "endTime": 51.84,
    "text": "entirely unvoiced"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.84,
    "endTime": 53.92,
    "text": "think about my mother for a minute when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.92,
    "endTime": 56.559,
    "text": "i was 15 i came home from school one day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.559,
    "endTime": 58.719,
    "text": "and she was standing on a long veranda"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.719,
    "endTime": 60.719,
    "text": "outside of our kitchen holding a giant"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.719,
    "endTime": 62.8,
    "text": "stack of plates"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.8,
    "endTime": 65.84,
    "text": "imagine how dumbfounded i was when she"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.84,
    "endTime": 69.6,
    "text": "started to throw them like frisbees"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.6,
    "endTime": 72.4,
    "text": "into the hot humid air"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.4,
    "endTime": 74.479,
    "text": "when every single plate had shattered"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.479,
    "endTime": 76.64,
    "text": "into thousands of pieces on the hill"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.64,
    "endTime": 79.52,
    "text": "below she walked back in and she said to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.52,
    "endTime": 83.359,
    "text": "me cheerfully how was your day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.6,
    "endTime": 88.88,
    "text": "now you can see you can see how a child"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.88,
    "endTime": 91.119,
    "text": "would look at an incident like this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.119,
    "endTime": 93.439,
    "text": "and think that anger is silent and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.439,
    "endTime": 95.52,
    "text": "isolating destructive and even"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.52,
    "endTime": 97.28,
    "text": "frightening"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.28,
    "endTime": 98.96,
    "text": "especially though"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.96,
    "endTime": 101.84,
    "text": "when the person who's angry is a girl or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.84,
    "endTime": 103.04,
    "text": "a woman"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.04,
    "endTime": 105.28,
    "text": "the question is why"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.28,
    "endTime": 107.759,
    "text": "anger is a human emotion neither good"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.759,
    "endTime": 109.2,
    "text": "nor bad"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.2,
    "endTime": 111.6,
    "text": "it is actually a signal emotion it warns"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.6,
    "endTime": 115.6,
    "text": "us of indignity threat insult and harm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.6,
    "endTime": 118.56,
    "text": "and yet in culture after culture"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.56,
    "endTime": 121.439,
    "text": "anger is reserved as the moral property"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.439,
    "endTime": 123.68,
    "text": "of boys and men"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.68,
    "endTime": 125.759,
    "text": "now to be sure there are differences so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.759,
    "endTime": 127.84,
    "text": "in the united states for example"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.84,
    "endTime": 131.039,
    "text": "an angry black man is viewed as a a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.039,
    "endTime": 133.36,
    "text": "criminal but an angry white man has"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.36,
    "endTime": 135.44,
    "text": "civic virtue"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.44,
    "endTime": 137.84,
    "text": "regardless of where we are however the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.84,
    "endTime": 139.76,
    "text": "emotion is gendered"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.76,
    "endTime": 143.2,
    "text": "and so we teach children to disdain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.2,
    "endTime": 145.44,
    "text": "anger in girls and women and we grow up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.44,
    "endTime": 147.2,
    "text": "to be adults"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.2,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "that penalize it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 152.56,
    "text": "so what if we didn't do that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.56,
    "endTime": 154.319,
    "text": "what if we didn't sever"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.319,
    "endTime": 156.879,
    "text": "anger from femininity because severing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.879,
    "endTime": 158.64,
    "text": "anger from femininity means we sever"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.64,
    "endTime": 160.959,
    "text": "girls and women from the emotion that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.959,
    "endTime": 163.44,
    "text": "best protects us from injustice"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.44,
    "endTime": 165.04,
    "text": "what if instead we thought about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.04,
    "endTime": 168.16,
    "text": "developing emotional competence for boys"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.16,
    "endTime": 169.68,
    "text": "and girls"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.68,
    "endTime": 172.16,
    "text": "the fact is we still remarkably"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.16,
    "endTime": 174.56,
    "text": "socialize children in very binary and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.56,
    "endTime": 176.48,
    "text": "oppositional ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.48,
    "endTime": 178.4,
    "text": "boys are held to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.4,
    "endTime": 181.599,
    "text": "absurd rigid norms of masculinity told"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.599,
    "endTime": 183.2,
    "text": "to sort of renounce the feminine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.2,
    "endTime": 185.76,
    "text": "emotionality of sadness or fear and to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.76,
    "endTime": 188.159,
    "text": "embrace aggression and anger as markers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.159,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "of real manhood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 191.519,
    "text": "on the other hand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.519,
    "endTime": 194.48,
    "text": "girls learn to be deferential"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.48,
    "endTime": 198.0,
    "text": "and anger is incompatible with deference"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.0,
    "endTime": 200.08,
    "text": "in the same way that we learn to cross"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.08,
    "endTime": 201.92,
    "text": "our legs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.92,
    "endTime": 204.08,
    "text": "and tame our hair"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.08,
    "endTime": 206.08,
    "text": "we learn to bite our tongues and swallow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.08,
    "endTime": 208.159,
    "text": "our pride"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.159,
    "endTime": 210.4,
    "text": "what happens too often"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.4,
    "endTime": 213.2,
    "text": "is that for all of us indignity becomes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.2,
    "endTime": 216.56,
    "text": "imminent in our notions of femininity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.56,
    "endTime": 218.879,
    "text": "there's a long personal and political"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.879,
    "endTime": 219.76,
    "text": "tale"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.76,
    "endTime": 222.159,
    "text": "to that bifurcation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.159,
    "endTime": 224.64,
    "text": "in anger we go from being"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.64,
    "endTime": 227.76,
    "text": "spoiled princesses and hormonal teens"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.76,
    "endTime": 230.799,
    "text": "to high maintenance women and shrill"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.799,
    "endTime": 232.4,
    "text": "ugly nags"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.4,
    "endTime": 235.12,
    "text": "we have flavors though pick your flavor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.12,
    "endTime": 237.599,
    "text": "are you a spicy hot latina when you're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.599,
    "endTime": 238.4,
    "text": "mad"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.4,
    "endTime": 240.72,
    "text": "or a sad asian girl"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.72,
    "endTime": 243.599,
    "text": "an angry black woman or a crazy white"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.599,
    "endTime": 245.599,
    "text": "one"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.599,
    "endTime": 247.04,
    "text": "you can pick"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.04,
    "endTime": 249.599,
    "text": "but in fact the effect is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.599,
    "endTime": 251.76,
    "text": "that when we say what's important to us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.76,
    "endTime": 254.48,
    "text": "which is what anger is conveying people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.48,
    "endTime": 256.799,
    "text": "are more likely to get angry at us for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.799,
    "endTime": 258.639,
    "text": "being angry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.639,
    "endTime": 261.519,
    "text": "whether we're at home or in school or at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.519,
    "endTime": 264.32,
    "text": "work or in a political arena"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.32,
    "endTime": 266.88,
    "text": "anger confirms masculinity and it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.88,
    "endTime": 268.88,
    "text": "confounds femininity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.88,
    "endTime": 271.68,
    "text": "so men are rewarded for displaying it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.68,
    "endTime": 273.759,
    "text": "and women are penalized for doing the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.759,
    "endTime": 275.84,
    "text": "same"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.84,
    "endTime": 278.479,
    "text": "this puts us at an enormous disadvantage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.479,
    "endTime": 280.24,
    "text": "particularly when we have to defend"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.24,
    "endTime": 283.52,
    "text": "ourselves and our own interests"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.52,
    "endTime": 285.199,
    "text": "if we're faced with a threatening street"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.199,
    "endTime": 288.4,
    "text": "harasser a predatory employer a sexist"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.4,
    "endTime": 290.24,
    "text": "racist classmate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.24,
    "endTime": 293.52,
    "text": "our brains are screaming are you kidding"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.52,
    "endTime": 294.8,
    "text": "me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.8,
    "endTime": 296.72,
    "text": "and our mouths say"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.72,
    "endTime": 299.6,
    "text": "i'm sorry what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.88,
    "endTime": 303.04,
    "text": "right"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.04,
    "endTime": 305.04,
    "text": "and it's conflicting because the anger"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.04,
    "endTime": 307.039,
    "text": "gets all tangled up with the anxiety and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.039,
    "endTime": 309.84,
    "text": "the fear and the risk and retaliation if"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.84,
    "endTime": 311.759,
    "text": "you ask women what they fear the most in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.759,
    "endTime": 313.919,
    "text": "response to their anger they don't say"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.919,
    "endTime": 317.12,
    "text": "violence they say mockery"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.12,
    "endTime": 320.32,
    "text": "think about what that means"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.4,
    "endTime": 322.32,
    "text": "if you have multiple marginalized"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.32,
    "endTime": 325.28,
    "text": "identities it's not just mockery if you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.28,
    "endTime": 327.36,
    "text": "defend yourself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.36,
    "endTime": 329.28,
    "text": "if you put a stake in the ground"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.28,
    "endTime": 332.0,
    "text": "there can be dire consequences"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.0,
    "endTime": 334.8,
    "text": "now we reproduce these patterns not in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.8,
    "endTime": 337.52,
    "text": "big bold and blunt ways but in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.52,
    "endTime": 338.479,
    "text": "everyday"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.479,
    "endTime": 340.88,
    "text": "banality of life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.88,
    "endTime": 343.12,
    "text": "when my daughter was in preschool every"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.12,
    "endTime": 345.52,
    "text": "single morning she built an elaborate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.52,
    "endTime": 348.16,
    "text": "castle ribbons and blocks and every"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.16,
    "endTime": 349.6,
    "text": "single morning the same boy knocked it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.6,
    "endTime": 351.6,
    "text": "down gleefully"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.6,
    "endTime": 353.84,
    "text": "his parents were there but they never"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.84,
    "endTime": 356.32,
    "text": "intervened before the fact"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.32,
    "endTime": 358.56,
    "text": "they were happy to provide platitudes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.56,
    "endTime": 360.16,
    "text": "afterwards"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.16,
    "endTime": 362.24,
    "text": "boys will be boys"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.24,
    "endTime": 364.84,
    "text": "it's so tempting he just couldn't help"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.84,
    "endTime": 367.44,
    "text": "himself i did"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.44,
    "endTime": 370.08,
    "text": "what many girls and women learned to do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.08,
    "endTime": 372.479,
    "text": "i preemptively kept the peace and i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.479,
    "endTime": 375.44,
    "text": "taught my daughter to do the same thing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.44,
    "endTime": 378.319,
    "text": "she used her words"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.319,
    "endTime": 380.96,
    "text": "she tried to gently body block him"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.96,
    "endTime": 382.96,
    "text": "she moved where she was building in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.96,
    "endTime": 385.759,
    "text": "classroom to no effect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.759,
    "endTime": 388.08,
    "text": "so i and the other adults"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.08,
    "endTime": 390.8,
    "text": "mutually constructed a particular male"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.8,
    "endTime": 392.319,
    "text": "entitlement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.319,
    "endTime": 394.24,
    "text": "he could run rampant and control the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 394.24,
    "endTime": 395.68,
    "text": "environment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.68,
    "endTime": 398.479,
    "text": "and she kept her feelings to herself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.479,
    "endTime": 401.039,
    "text": "and worked around his needs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.039,
    "endTime": 403.039,
    "text": "we failed both of them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.039,
    "endTime": 405.68,
    "text": "by not giving her anger the uptake and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.68,
    "endTime": 408.56,
    "text": "resolution that it deserved now that's a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.56,
    "endTime": 411.759,
    "text": "microcosm of a much bigger problem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.759,
    "endTime": 413.759,
    "text": "because culturally"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.759,
    "endTime": 415.919,
    "text": "worldwide"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 415.919,
    "endTime": 417.44,
    "text": "we preference"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.44,
    "endTime": 419.84,
    "text": "the performance of masculinity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.84,
    "endTime": 421.44,
    "text": "and the power and privilege that come"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.44,
    "endTime": 423.039,
    "text": "with that performance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 423.039,
    "endTime": 425.919,
    "text": "over the rights and needs and words of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.919,
    "endTime": 428.8,
    "text": "children and women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.88,
    "endTime": 430.639,
    "text": "so it will come as absolutely no"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.639,
    "endTime": 432.479,
    "text": "surprise probably to the people in this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 432.479,
    "endTime": 433.28,
    "text": "room"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.28,
    "endTime": 436.639,
    "text": "that women report being angrier in more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.639,
    "endTime": 439.28,
    "text": "sustained ways and with more intensity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 439.28,
    "endTime": 441.68,
    "text": "than men do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441.68,
    "endTime": 442.96,
    "text": "some of that comes from the fact that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 442.96,
    "endTime": 444.96,
    "text": "we're socialized to ruminate to keep it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.96,
    "endTime": 447.68,
    "text": "to ourselves and mullet over"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.68,
    "endTime": 450.24,
    "text": "but we also have to find socially"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 450.24,
    "endTime": 453.199,
    "text": "palatable ways to express the intensity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.199,
    "endTime": 455.199,
    "text": "of emotion that we have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.199,
    "endTime": 457.84,
    "text": "and the awareness that it brings of our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 457.84,
    "endTime": 459.52,
    "text": "precarity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.52,
    "endTime": 462.08,
    "text": "so we do several things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 462.08,
    "endTime": 464.639,
    "text": "if men knew how often women were filled"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.639,
    "endTime": 467.52,
    "text": "with white hot rage when we cried"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.52,
    "endTime": 470.8,
    "text": "they would be staggered"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470.96,
    "endTime": 472.96,
    "text": "we use minimizing language"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.96,
    "endTime": 477.479,
    "text": "we're frustrated no really it's okay"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.199,
    "endTime": 481.199,
    "text": "self-objectify and lose the ability to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.199,
    "endTime": 484.319,
    "text": "even recognize the physiological"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484.319,
    "endTime": 487.68,
    "text": "changes that indicate anger"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 487.68,
    "endTime": 491.039,
    "text": "mainly though we get sick"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.039,
    "endTime": 494.479,
    "text": "anger has now been implicated in a whole"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.479,
    "endTime": 496.4,
    "text": "array of illnesses that are casually"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 496.4,
    "endTime": 499.12,
    "text": "dismissed as women's illnesses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.12,
    "endTime": 501.28,
    "text": "higher rates of chronic pain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.28,
    "endTime": 503.039,
    "text": "autoimmune disorders"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.039,
    "endTime": 504.72,
    "text": "disordered eating"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 504.72,
    "endTime": 507.36,
    "text": "mental distress anxiety self-harm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.36,
    "endTime": 509.199,
    "text": "depression"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.199,
    "endTime": 511.28,
    "text": "anger affects our immune systems our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.28,
    "endTime": 513.36,
    "text": "cardiovascular systems"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.36,
    "endTime": 515.839,
    "text": "some studies even indicate that it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.839,
    "endTime": 518.32,
    "text": "affects mortality rates particularly in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.32,
    "endTime": 521.839,
    "text": "black women with cancer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.24,
    "endTime": 525.36,
    "text": "i am sick and tired of the women i know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 525.36,
    "endTime": 528.56,
    "text": "being sick and tired"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.12,
    "endTime": 532.16,
    "text": "our anger brings great discomfort"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.16,
    "endTime": 534.56,
    "text": "and the conflict comes because it's our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.56,
    "endTime": 537.279,
    "text": "role to bring comfort"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537.279,
    "endTime": 539.2,
    "text": "there is anger that's acceptable we can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539.2,
    "endTime": 540.399,
    "text": "be angry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.399,
    "endTime": 541.36,
    "text": "when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.36,
    "endTime": 542.24,
    "text": "we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.24,
    "endTime": 544.24,
    "text": "stay in our lanes and buttress a status"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.24,
    "endTime": 545.12,
    "text": "quo"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.12,
    "endTime": 549.279,
    "text": "as mothers or teachers we can be mad but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 549.279,
    "endTime": 551.36,
    "text": "we can't be angry about the tremendous"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.36,
    "endTime": 553.76,
    "text": "costs of nurturing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.76,
    "endTime": 555.92,
    "text": "we can be angry at our mothers let's say"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.92,
    "endTime": 558.32,
    "text": "as teenagers patriarchal rules and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 558.32,
    "endTime": 560.48,
    "text": "regulations we don't blame systems we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.48,
    "endTime": 562.48,
    "text": "blame them we can be angry at other"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562.48,
    "endTime": 564.72,
    "text": "women because who doesn't love a good"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.72,
    "endTime": 566.32,
    "text": "cat fight"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.32,
    "endTime": 568.88,
    "text": "and we can be angry at men with lower"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.88,
    "endTime": 572.16,
    "text": "status in an expressive hierarchy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 572.16,
    "endTime": 575.68,
    "text": "that supports racism or xenophobia"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 575.68,
    "endTime": 578.32,
    "text": "but we have an enormous power in this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.32,
    "endTime": 581.76,
    "text": "because feelings are the purview of our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.76,
    "endTime": 583.519,
    "text": "authority"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 583.519,
    "endTime": 585.36,
    "text": "and people are uncomfortable with our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.36,
    "endTime": 586.8,
    "text": "anger"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 586.8,
    "endTime": 589.36,
    "text": "we should be making people comfortable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.36,
    "endTime": 591.92,
    "text": "with the discomfort they feel when women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.92,
    "endTime": 593.04,
    "text": "say no"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.04,
    "endTime": 595.839,
    "text": "unapologetically"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 595.839,
    "endTime": 598.48,
    "text": "we can take emotions and think in terms"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 598.48,
    "endTime": 601.44,
    "text": "of competence and not gender"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.44,
    "endTime": 603.68,
    "text": "people who are able to process their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603.68,
    "endTime": 605.68,
    "text": "anger and make meaning from it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 605.68,
    "endTime": 608.88,
    "text": "are more creative more optimistic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.88,
    "endTime": 610.8,
    "text": "they have more intimacy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.8,
    "endTime": 614.16,
    "text": "they're better problem solvers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 614.16,
    "endTime": 617.12,
    "text": "they have greater political efficacy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617.12,
    "endTime": 618.48,
    "text": "now i'm a woman"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.48,
    "endTime": 621.04,
    "text": "writing about women and feelings so very"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.04,
    "endTime": 623.04,
    "text": "few men with power"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.04,
    "endTime": 624.56,
    "text": "are going to take what i'm saying"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.56,
    "endTime": 627.76,
    "text": "seriously as a matter of politics"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 627.76,
    "endTime": 630.48,
    "text": "we think of politics and anger in terms"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.48,
    "endTime": 632.56,
    "text": "of the contempt and disdain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.56,
    "endTime": 635.12,
    "text": "and and fury that are feeding a rise of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.12,
    "endTime": 637.279,
    "text": "macho fascism in the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 637.279,
    "endTime": 639.6,
    "text": "but if it's that poison it's also the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.6,
    "endTime": 641.44,
    "text": "antidote"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.44,
    "endTime": 643.76,
    "text": "we have an anger of hope and we see it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.76,
    "endTime": 645.279,
    "text": "every single day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.279,
    "endTime": 647.76,
    "text": "in the resistant anger of women and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.76,
    "endTime": 649.68,
    "text": "marginalized people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649.68,
    "endTime": 653.04,
    "text": "it's related to compassion and empathy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 653.04,
    "endTime": 654.24,
    "text": "and love"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 654.24,
    "endTime": 656.8,
    "text": "and we should recognize that anger as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656.8,
    "endTime": 659.04,
    "text": "well"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 659.519,
    "endTime": 661.6,
    "text": "the issue is that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661.6,
    "endTime": 663.92,
    "text": "societies that don't respect women's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 663.92,
    "endTime": 664.88,
    "text": "anger"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.88,
    "endTime": 667.44,
    "text": "don't respect women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 667.44,
    "endTime": 670.959,
    "text": "the real danger of our anger isn't that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 670.959,
    "endTime": 675.12,
    "text": "it will break bonds or plates it's that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.12,
    "endTime": 678.16,
    "text": "it exactly shows how seriously we take"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 678.16,
    "endTime": 681.44,
    "text": "ourselves and we expect other people to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 681.44,
    "endTime": 684.0,
    "text": "take us seriously as well"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 684.0,
    "endTime": 686.0,
    "text": "when that happens"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 686.0,
    "endTime": 688.8,
    "text": "chances are very good that women will be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 688.8,
    "endTime": 690.48,
    "text": "able to smile"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.48,
    "endTime": 693.44,
    "text": "when they want to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 694.64,
    "endTime": 697.88,
    "text": "thank you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.519,
    "endTime": 705.6,
    "text": "you"
  }
]